(469, 1, '2022-10-04 23:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p>1648-1685<br />\nFollowing one family from its roots in a remote island in 17th-century Sussex, across more than two centuries to Europe and the United States, the Fairmile series illuminates how everyday women found dynasties and shape history.</p>\n', '', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2022-10-04 23:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'https://ebohrman.bitlampsites.com/wpd/homework/?p=469', 1, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
(470, 1, '2022-10-04 23:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p>1772-1805<br />\nBeatrice Lacey, as strong-minded as she is beautiful, refuses to conform to the social customs of her time. Destined to lose her family name and beloved Wideacre estate once she is wed, Beatrice will use any means necessary to protect her ancestral heritage.</p>\n', '', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2022-10-04 23:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'https://ebohrman.bitlampsites.com/wpd/homework/?p=470', 1, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
(471, 1, '2022-10-04 23:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p>1460-1461<br />\nA young woman named Isabel strives to reclaim the birthright of her family estate from her conniving brother. She and her Saracen servant Ishraq embark upon a journey to do so and run into a young novice-in-training, the “changeling” of our story, named Luca and his trusty scribe.</p>\n', '', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2022-10-04 23:55:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'https://ebohrman.bitlampsites.com/wpd/homework/?p=471', 1, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
